column100: We are looking for an extra dishwasher for our team at Christianshavn's ferry cafe. We are located in the center of Copenhagen. The job is 40-60 hours a month and is mainly in the evenings and on weekends. It is important that you can work both weekday evenings and weekends. A shift usually starts at 16:00 and ends around 23:00 earlier weekdays and on weekends around midnight.  In the summer this day shift as well. You will be part of a team of 4-5 peolpe so you flixeblity is importen. You will typically have 1-3 shifts per week. If you are a student it is an advantage but not a requirement
